| Property | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Image ratio | 16:9 |
| Corner radius | 24px |
| Badge (optional) | Top-left: Featured, Award Winning, etc. |
| Title | Max 2 lines |
| Description | Max 3 lines on grid cards |
| Entire card | Clickable |

